{"tid":691759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司將就涉及梁天琦的一項暴動罪重審","createTime":"2018-06-06T04:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T03:49:22.000Z","uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e161ff0b6ae64391b87381226f9ecebfdcd9c94b","tid":691759,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前年大年初二凌晨旺角發生騷亂，本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦等5人被控煽惑暴動及參與暴動等罪，案件早前審訊，陪審團未能就被告梁天琦、李諾文及林傲軒涉及的一項暴動罪達成裁決。辯方於上周五收到律政司通知，指已決定就該項控罪重審，案件將於7月18日預審。<br />\n<br />\n陪審團於上月18日一致裁定梁天琦煽惑暴動罪脫，一項指他於亞皆老街參與暴動罪成，而梁早已承認一項襲警罪，法官將於下周一判刑。<br />\n<br />\n將會重審的控罪指三被告於砵蘭街參與暴動，控方早前曾透露，若果案件重審，或與另外一宗定於今年11月開審的旺角騷亂案件合併處理，該案其中一名被告為「美國隊長」容偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180606/58283373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58283373&d=vhjfVoIsUf8uppYeFv%2B2ITACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=64e16841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58283373&h=bbc329aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180606/58283373</a>"},{"pid":"2b50c2cddd91d11d8042c4820b5fbbaab62903ea","tid":691759,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"708d6dcd4931118e348036b9b9a63f4ba054def2","tid":691759,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e24b58a5bea606d324a4b1a8107caf926677f92","tid":691759,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803b5ec64febf1d9663b91d00789a720f0fa2229","tid":691759,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"708d6dcd4931